Sec. 8-76. - Administrative fees for independent agents and brokers. 
Independent agencies and brokers, for each separate business location from which business is conducted in the City that is not subject to a company administrative fee under the provisions of this article, shall pay an annual administrative fee in the amount established by the City Council. The administrative fee assessed in this section is due January 1 of each year. 
