(85)  West Watson Street where it intersects with Godfrey Street; 
(86)  West Watson Street where it intersects with Wesley Street; 
(87)  Whatcoat Street where it intersects with George Street; 
(88)  Whatcoat Street where it intersects with Pierce Street; 
(89)  Williams Street where it intersects with Asbury Street; 
(90)  Williams Street where it intersects with Wesley Street. 
(b)  All persons traveling on the streets shall come to a dead stop before entering on through streets and shall give right-of-way to persons traveling on through-streets. 
(Ord. of 12-5-2011(05), § 11-110; Ord. of 8-6-2012(02), § 1(11-108)) 
